step1: open VM
step2: click on ubuntu setting 
         select network
step3: make adaptor1 as NAT 
step4: run both OS 
step5: open terminal in both and then
          run command " sudo apt install net-tools "

step6: create on file in one OS ("file.txt")
step7: check IP Address with " ifconfig " command 

step8: then to send file 
         " scp file.txt first_name@10.0.2.4: "  command 
